text: I have been to MT A couple of weeks ago suffering from severe dental pain and infection arising from my wisdom tooth, the swelling around my jaw complicated my tooth extraction due to limited mouth opening and other dental clinics were no ready to do the procedure. Finally, i met Dr. Goh during my specialist consultation. he assured me of safe removal and extracted my tooth with great skill and zero discomfort. all my pain, infection and swelling were gone in next 3 days. Thanks, a lot to Dr. Goh. he is a Gem.
The staffs are friendly, compassionate & accommodating. A pleasant experience thus far!
